                <head/>
                <origin>Alexandria Gazette</origin>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Questions the secessionists dedication to states' rights when the most
                    radical of their wing wish to disregard the voice of the people of Virginia, who
                    voted for pro-Union delegates to the Convention in the recent election.</summary>
                <note/>
